➜惊！万万没想到鸡排还能炒着吃？好吃到爆炸！
http://www.sohu.com/a/416220978_100001467	8447
<p class="ql-align-center">喜欢吃鸡排🌶️的亲们福利来啦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样做比😋部队锅还要好吃💥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天试试💕家庭版的薯条🧀️炒鸡排</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">好吃到爆炸~😍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200903/05aaf03f5f104e8c8eb08427c2210e9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今天把炒鸡排黄金食谱告诉大家，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让大家足不出户，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也能品尝美味的薯条炒鸡排！！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">🥘第一步：大希地糠糠大鸡排无需解冻，拿出后直接下锅炸3-5分钟至两面金黄；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200903/7b41790dd2dc48bb8cce5726b22b7af2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第二步：选一颗大土豆，切条，表面裹一层面粉，下锅炸至金黄；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200903/de455c2ab40243aab74c9b75662cd658.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">第三步：把炸好的大鸡排切条；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200903/1feec4f08a1f4f1ea1884b2fa39a5003.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">炸好的薯条捞出沥油备用；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200903/6cc9ca4ba09d434abb53063692345722.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第四步：锅内放少许油，油热后放入蒜末爆香；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再放入炸好的土豆条翻炒1-2分钟；</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后放入切好的鸡排翻炒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">加点黑胡椒、辣椒粉、椒盐粉调味，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再翻炒均匀即可出锅~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200903/3447d33cf93c4afe8b2e02088d839694.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">🥗喜欢香菜的亲们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出锅前撒点香菜碎调味装饰一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不喜欢香菜味道的可以跳过这一步~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200903/6c5624f5df0a4a30b60b191ca012edd5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后一步：出锅装盘即可开吃啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡排和薯条都金黄诱人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蒜蓉和香菜的香气又让香味提升了几个档次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只闻着就流口水啦！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200903/4aa74151f35d4e159cdf759956010d32.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自己炸的薯条，酥糯可口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸡排外皮酥脆，内里软嫩多汁</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样一盘美味的薯条炒鸡排</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不考验厨艺、无需耗费过多时间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">10分钟内都能搞的定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">😍色香味俱全！！😍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200903/914433a1d11044f785219f2998d3d783.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有任何人能拒绝这样一盘飘香四溢的美味！😍</p>